file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 20-30-03-02 - ADHESIVES AND SEALANTS - MAINTENANCE PRACTICES

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL ADHESIVES AND SEALANTS - MAINTENANCE PRACTICES EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. This subchapter gives a list of the approved products that you can use on and service the aircraft, with their most usual suppliers. B. The correct procedure that uses these products must be referred to in the given chapters. C. Products with the same specification, MIL-, FED. SPEC, but from different manufacturers must not be mixed. D. Possible alternative products are listed in the same group of chapters that give the indicated product. E. Products listed on the QPL (Qualified Products List) for MIL Specifications, referred to in this subchapter, are automatically approved to be used on the aircraft. F. The supplier/manufacturer addresses are listed in AMM MPP 20-30-00/200. EMB-145 - AMM 1285 General 20-30-03 Page 1 of 13 Rev 55 - Oct 29/18 Copyright ÃÂ© by Embraer S.A.
